{
  "stem": "25639.9",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they sent me beautiful things, which permitted me to dress nicely while I was in Europe-- unusual clothes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- but I forgot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After the Holocaust, I was totally blank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I couldn't remember anything more than their names and the city in which they lived in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we didn't have a 911.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have a 411.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't have the directory and the operator assistance that we have today.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "God bless this industrial revolution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And there was no way that I could find out what-- what their addresses were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Furthermore, I had no idea whether the United States was bombed to pulp, as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had no idea, since I was completely blank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were uninformed about the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of course, we knew that the US won, the-- the Allies won the war, but the details were missing still.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So one night-- Gulan and I shared one room in twin beds and I woke up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, Gulan, Gulan, I just dreamt that my uncle's address was such and such Del Mar, St.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Louis, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She says, write it down, because by tomorrow morning, you won't remember it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I wondered where she-- how wise she was that she made me do that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I just dutifully wrote it down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She handed me pencil and paper, and the following morning, she commanded me to write a letter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figured, well, I have nothing to lose, maybe-- maybe this is it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, my uncle received my letter, and I missed it by two numbers within the same block.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, he contacted my aunt-- my other aunt was-- died in the meantime, and the whole family throughout the country, and I was the first one to show a sign of life.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
